EU Says Spain Has Made Major Progress, Reflecting Rapid Response

-- B y   A n d r e w   C l a p h a m
-- 
2011-10-11T10:36:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-11/eu-says-spain-has-made-major-progress-reflecting-rapid-response.html
Spain  has made “major” progress in
terms of fiscal consolidation and structural reform reflecting a
“rapid” response to the problems on the markets over the
summer, European Commission spokeswoman Pia Ahrenkilde Hansen
told reporters in Brussels today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
